reviews.text: This is one of the malls belonging to the Link group. Typical setting and similar variety of restaurants and shops. It's pretty convenient for the local neighborhood to get groceries, food, and the basic necessities they need. You can't complain about it as it's different from the big shopping mall located in Kowloon and the island side.
Place has been clean up with a new wet market but so have the price. Good place to buy what you need if you are in the area. Has heaps of small restaurant
Small but nice mall with lots of goodie can be found here.
Enjoyed visiting! Nice local scene, with fresh foods on display.
There is a lot of ships in there but there us a wet market nearby so I think the hygiene is a little poor

reviews.text: 老村優化👍

改裝個商場都ok ，但下面嘅玻璃門麻麻地好難推開對門，因為如果啲公公婆婆揸拐杖入呢個商場就困難啲;街市嗰面就方便; 因為係自動門。
地方大，全新裝修後購物多左好多選擇
地下新裝修後，多咗食市和新街市，選購衣物和食物也算好地方！

reviews.text: A more "premium" Cantonese restaurant. Very friendly and helpful staff. Servings are suitable. Food quality is very decent too!
食物水準非常一般， 叉燒包的叉燒有疑似不新鮮味道。 棉花雞味道尚算可以 ， 燒賣算好食，｡服務員溝通不足， 食物追了又追，等了又等！！
早茶價錢大眾化，點心食物一般，如不苛求可以接受，就是比較嘈雜，侍應招呼則一般。
食物味道同份量都值一讚，服務員態度也理想，只有地毯清潔較差
味道及菜式一般，大時大節會漏單激死人
